\title{Access to Twitter Streaming API via R.} 
\description{
A package base on \link{streamR} package which provides a set of functions that allow R users to access Twitter's stream API. The package \code{\link{tweet2r}} has  a function to capture tweets using Twitter streaming API two functions to export the tweets to PostgreSQL , Sqlite shp, GML or KML and a function to get a summary of the tweets retrieved. Also there is a function to validate the JSON files where the tweets has been stored}

